<title type="html"><![CDATA[The PPU has an even/odd flag, the wiki says.. where?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4837&amp;p=42991#p42991"><![CDATA[
You either count cycles, or do the stupid trial-error-nintendulator method:<br /><br />get remotely close to the number of cycles you need, find out what pixel Nintendulator says you're at, then compensate by taking away or adding several cycles if you're not in hblank.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Fri Feb 06, 2009 11:31 pm</p><hr />
